title: USDA ERS,  the U.S. Pork imports by month by country, Jan 08 to Feb 09
name: USDA ERS,  the U.S. Pork imports by month by country, Jan 08 to Feb 09
description:
The poly shapefile shows monthly imports of pork from countries to the U.S. The original tabular data was extracted from USDA's ERS (Economic Reseach Service) and then georeferenced. Since the outbreak of swine flu in Mexico and sporadic cases seen in the U.S., there is increased concern over the import/export of pork products. It has already resulted in Russia and China banning all pork product imports from the U.S. and Mexico.

Note: All imports in thousand of pounds.
